"pid":"c76a8d66f514cfd639a14ca05a29655d63ea4e2f","tid":753920,"uid":117275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0e7f71404445c65cdb7939faf9ef6241427967b","tid":753920,"uid":140060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"如果你話成set線係早一兩日換，彈左冇耐，甚至係冇彈過就斷左條嘅話，就咁買多條1線都ok，因為成set線overall都仲係新；<br />\n但如果你話set線係彈左一兩個月，然後依家先黎斷左條嘅話，就建議你成set換，因為你攞條全新嘅1線，配5條用左成個月嘅線，個聲同condition都會唔夾，同埋反正其他線都用左咁耐，唔差在換埋佢地。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:12:21.000Z","msg":"感謝解答!"},{"pid":"b348436d77c78b3709026b15ce50d114c5f76bbc","tid":753920,"uid":140060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪結他新手？提多你一樣野，下次換線時，可以順便用鉛筆/鉛芯筆畫一畫結他個nut（上弦枕）嘅線坑，有助減少磨擦力，從而減少斷線同走音嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n下圖為示範：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/142200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F142200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fdd8d940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果巴打係多汗人士，或者唔想成日換線，可以買 Elixir 呢個牌子嘅線，佢木同電結他都有做，特色係佢地嘅線有一層好薄嘅膠膜包住，聲可能會比一般嘅線矇少少，但計整體壽命同手感，我都覺得係好過普通線。<br />\n<br />\n木結他線：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/143016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F143016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e50ce13f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電結他線：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/143039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F143039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a4838b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢隻線通利同柏斯都有做，有唔同string guage揀，至於佢嗰3隻唔同嘅包膠方式（nanoweb, optiweb, polyweb)都係差唔多，求其揀一隻就得。不過佢呢隻就冇單條買，我斷左條嘅話都係買Daddario頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有興趣可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61db1df21593798348017f51debe503478c78c5f","tid":753920,"uid":140060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b348436d77c78b3709026b15ce50d114c5f76bbc","tid":753920,"uid":140060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪結他新手？提多你一樣野，下次換線時，可以順便用鉛筆/鉛芯筆畫一畫結他個nut（上弦枕）嘅線坑，有助減少磨擦力，從而減少斷線同走音嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n下圖為示範：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/142200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F142200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fdd8d940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果巴打係多汗人士，或者唔想成日換線，可以買 Elixir 呢個牌子嘅線，佢木同電結他都有做，特色係佢地嘅線有一層好薄嘅膠膜包住，聲可能會比一般嘅線矇少少，但計整體壽命同手感，我都覺得係好過普通線。<br />\n<br />\n木結他線：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/143016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F143016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e50ce13f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電結他線：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/143039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F143039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a4838b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢隻線通利同柏斯都有做，有唔同string guage揀，至於佢嗰3隻唔同嘅包膠方式（nanoweb, optiweb, polyweb)都係差唔多，求其揀一隻就得。不過佢呢隻就冇單條買，我斷左條嘅話都係買Daddario頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有興趣可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/143401_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F143401_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=76fe41d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幅示範圖消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5ae88d68f45a817a126937b28da507018686df","tid":753920,"uid":117275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b348436d77c78b3709026b15ce50d114c5f76bbc","tid":753920,"uid":140060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪結他新手？提多你一樣野，下次換線時，可以順便用鉛筆/鉛芯筆畫一畫結他個nut（上弦枕）嘅線坑，有助減少磨擦力，從而減少斷線同走音嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n下圖為示範：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/142200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F142200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fdd8d940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果巴打係多汗人士，或者唔想成日換線，可以買 Elixir 呢個牌子嘅線，佢木同電結他都有做，特色係佢地嘅線有一層好薄嘅膠膜包住，聲可能會比一般嘅線矇少少，但計整體壽命同手感，我都覺得係好過普通線。<br />\n<br />\n木結他線：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/143016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F143016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e50ce13f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電結他線：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/143039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F143039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a4838b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢隻線通利同柏斯都有做，有唔同string guage揀，至於佢嗰3隻唔同嘅包膠方式（nanoweb, optiweb, polyweb)都係差唔多，求其揀一隻就得。不過佢呢隻就冇單條買，我斷左條嘅話都係買Daddario頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有興趣可以去睇下<img src=